<item>
            <title>[LU-2068] configure option &quot;--without-ldiskfs&quot; does not build.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2068</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I run into build issues with the &quot;lvfs&quot; directory and the &quot;osd-ldiskfs&quot; directory if I configure the tree using the &quot;--without-ldiskfs&quot; option.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Lustre Tree: 2.3.51-7-g1d7fa63&lt;br/&gt;
OS: CHAOS 5 (RHEL 6.2)</environment>
        <key id="16204">LU-2068</key>
            <summary>configure option &quot;--without-ldiskfs&quot; does not build.</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=11303&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
